<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #1e40af; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .button { background: #1e40af; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
        </div>
        
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering with Personal Wings! Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p><a href="{{verificationUrl}}">{{verificationUrl}}</a></p>
        
        <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you didn't create an account with Personal Wings, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>